297
00:25:23,119 --> 00:25:25,379
You're the lucky ones.

298
00:25:48,819 --> 00:25:50,619
Jiang Qiao Xi.

299
00:25:51,619 --> 00:25:55,040
Cherry.

300
00:26:00,460 --> 00:26:02,260
Jiang Qiao Xi.

301
00:26:08,859 --> 00:26:14,559
What's wrong, Cherry? Are you a repeater?

302
00:26:17,099 --> 00:26:24,359
