"How can Lin Cherry's voice be so sweet?"

307
00:27:02,119 --> 00:27:03,839
No taste.

308
00:27:03,839 --> 00:27:09,760
Cherry, all these years,

309
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:15,780
I've been trying to prove that I'm Jiang Qiao Xi.

310
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:20,420
Before, I had good grades.

311
00:27:20,420 --> 00:27:25,819
Used silence to abandon math,
relinquish guaranteed admissions.

312
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:37,859
Even... even used that method
to prove I'm Jiang Qiao Xi.

313
00:27:39,859 --> 00:27:42,119
But now I suddenly realize

314
00:27:42,119 --> 00:27:50,539
the moment I heard you call my name,
I truly existed.

315
00:29:52,420 --> 00:29:54,519
Hello.

316
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:56,352
Qin Ye Yun.

317
00:30:02,336 --> 00:30:07,220
I'm in Hong Kong.

318
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:08,720
I know.

319
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:13,659
