320
00:30:15,259 --> 00:30:21,440
I know that. Lin Cherry, it's 3 AM right now.

321
00:30:25,740 --> 00:30:27,540
I...

322
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:34,399
I get it. Are you feeling happy or not right now?

323
00:30:39,500 --> 00:30:45,960
I don't know if I'm happy or not.

324
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:51,090
 Just feel... 

325
00:30:51,968 --> 00:30:55,260
different from before,

326
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:58,619
but somehow everything remains the same.

327
00:30:58,619 --> 00:31:00,759
