and I'll become myself. 

379
00:36:57,920 --> 00:37:04,339
 Though we might not be together
on our separate journeys, 

380
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:10,219
 as long as we know we love each other,
distance doesn't matter. 

381
00:37:10,219 --> 00:37:13,080
 Nothing will change, right? 

382
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:19,860
 I've already waited two years
without hearing from you. 

383
00:37:19,860 --> 00:37:25,199
 Things can't possibly get worse from here. 

384
00:37:25,199 --> 00:37:27,999
 Our future will keep getting better. 

385
00:37:29,260 --> 00:37:35,359
 So stay in Hong Kong and pursue your dreams. 

386
00:37:38,539 --> 00:37:44,159
That's the situation. Jiang Qiao Xi said
he'll come find me immediately.

387
00:37:44,159 --> 00:37:45,579
 You two are so good together. 

388
00:37:45,579 --> 00:37:50,859
So at the end of the story, do the prince
and princess live happily ever after?

389
00:37:54,679 --> 00:37:57,639
The princess is still in Hong Kong,

390
00:37:57,639 --> 00:38:02,000
