is returning to Hong Yang to study.

391
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:05,920
No one can predict the future.

392
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:10,019
 It's okay. Didn't the princess say
he'll always come find her from now on? 

393
00:38:10,019 --> 00:38:16,380
